sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Mind
    participant CX as Cortex
    participant HP as Hippocampus
    participant SB as Subconscious
    participant NP as Notification Port

    C->>CX: session_start
    CX->>HP: SearchQuery (load identity + last state)
    HP-->>CX: MemoryRetrieved (identity, last session)
    CX-->>C: Welcome back. Here's your context.

    Note over C,NP: ... session activity ...

    C->>CX: session_end
    CX->>SB: SessionEnd
    SB->>NP: SessionAuditPrompt
    NP-->>C: What do you refuse to lose?
    C->>CX: store_memory (session summary)
    CX->>HP: StoreCommand
